<o:TextSymbol Id="o33">
<a:Text>He thong Cloud Airline - Actor: Guest</a:Text>
<a:CreationDate>1783046611</a:CreationDate>
<a:ModificationDate>1783046611</a:ModificationDate>
<a:Rect>((-8000,29000), (6000,31000))</a:Rect>
<a:TextStyle>4130</a:TextStyle>
<a:AutoAdjustToText>0</a:AutoAdjustToText>
<a:LineColor>0</a:LineColor>
<a:DashStyle>7</a:DashStyle>
<a:FillColor>0</a:FillColor>
<a:ShadowColor>12632256</a:ShadowColor>
<a:FontName>Arial,10,B</a:FontName>
<a:ManuallyResized>1</a:ManuallyResized>
</o:TextSymbol>
</c:Symbols>
</o:UseCaseDiagram>
</c:UseCaseDiagrams>
<c:Actors>
<o:Actor Id="o21">
<a:ObjectID>FB001010-BB01-4B01-BB01-FB0010010010</a:ObjectID>
<a:Name>Guest</a:Name>
<a:Code>Guest</a:Code>
<a:CreationDate>1783046611</a:CreationDate>
<a:Creator>khoa</a:Creator>
<a:ModificationDate>1783046611</a:ModificationDate>
<a:Modifier>khoa</a:Modifier>
<a:Comment>Khach vang lai chua dang nhap. Co the tim chuyen bay, dat ve (chon ghe, nhap thong tin, thanh toan), huy ve bang ma booking + CMND/Passport, hoac dang ky tai khoan thanh vien.</a:Comment>
</o:Actor>
</c:Actors>
<c:UseCases>
<o:UseCase Id="o22">
<a:ObjectID>FB001020-BB01-4B01-BB01-FB0010010020</a:ObjectID>
<a:Name>Tim kiem chuyen bay</a:Name>
<a:Code>UC01_Tim_kiem_chuyen_bay</a:Code>
<a:CreationDate>1783046611</a:CreationDate>
<a:Creator>khoa</a:Creator>
<a:ModificationDate>1783046611</a:ModificationDate>
<a:Modifier>khoa</a:Modifier>
<a:Comment>Guest nhap diem di, diem den, ngay bay, so hanh khach, loai ve (1 chieu/khu hoi). He thong tra ve danh sach chuyen bay phu hop voi so ghe con trong theo tung hang. API: GET /api/flights.php. Screen: screen-search to screen-select-flight.</a:Comment>
</o:UseCase>
<o:UseCase Id="o23">
<a:ObjectID>FB001021-BB01-4B01-BB01-FB0010010021</a:ObjectID>
<a:Name>Dat ve may bay</a:Name>
<a:Code>UC02_Dat_ve_may_bay</a:Code>
<a:CreationDate>1783046611</a:CreationDate>
<a:Creator>khoa</a:Creator>
<a:ModificationDate>1783046611</a:ModificationDate>
<a:Modifier>khoa</a:Modifier>
<a:Comment>Guest chon chuyen bay, hang ghe (SkyBoss/Eco/Promo), nhap thong tin hanh khach, chon ghe va thanh toan. He thong tao ma booking dang CH-XXXXXX, luu vao DB voi user_id = NULL (khach vang lai). API: POST /api/book.php. Include: UC01, UC03.</a:Comment>
</o:UseCase>
<o:UseCase Id="o24">
<a:ObjectID>FB001022-BB01-4B01-BB01-FB0010010022</a:ObjectID>
<a:Name>Chon ghe ngoi</a:Name>
<a:Code>UC03_Chon_ghe_ngoi</a:Code>
<a:CreationDate>1783046611</a:CreationDate>
<a:Creator>khoa</a:Creator>
<a:ModificationDate>1783046611</a:ModificationDate>
<a:Modifier>khoa</a:Modifier>
<a:Comment>Guest chon ghe cu the tren so do cho ngoi. He thong giu cho tam trong 30 phut (countdown timer dung localStorage voi absolute deadline). Ghe da dat boi nguoi khac hien mau xam bi khoa. API: GET /api/booked_seats.php. Screen: screen-seats.</a:Comment>
</o:UseCase>
<o:UseCase Id="o25">
<a:ObjectID>FB001023-BB01-4B01-BB01-FB0010010023</a:ObjectID>
<a:Name>Huy ve bang ma booking</a:Name>
<a:Code>UC04_Huy_ve_bang_ma_booking</a:Code>
<a:CreationDate>1783046611</a:CreationDate>
<a:Creator>khoa</a:Creator>
<a:ModificationDate>1783046611</a:ModificationDate>
<a:Modifier>khoa</a:Modifier>
<a:Comment>Guest huy ve KHONG can dang nhap bang cach nhap ma booking (CH-XXXXXX) + so CMND/Passport cua mot trong cac hanh khach tren ve. He thong xac minh va cap nhat trang thai ve thanh Cancelled. Chi ap dung cho ve co user_id IS NULL. API: POST /api/cancel_booking_guest.php. Screen: screen-guest-cancel.</a:Comment>
</o:UseCase>
<o:UseCase Id="o26">
<a:ObjectID>FB001024-BB01-4B01-BB01-FB0010010024</a:ObjectID>
<a:Name>Dang ky tai khoan</a:Name>
<a:Code>UC05_Dang_ky_tai_khoan</a:Code>
<a:CreationDate>1783046611</a:CreationDate>
<a:Creator>khoa</a:Creator>
<a:ModificationDate>1783046611</a:ModificationDate>
<a:Modifier>khoa</a:Modifier>
<a:Comment>Guest tao tai khoan thanh vien moi bang email va mat khau. Role mac dinh luon la user - khong ai tu dang ky lam admin duoc (kiem soat trong register.php dong 30). Sau khi dang ky thanh cong, Guest chuyen thanh User. API: POST /api/register.php. Screen: screen-auth tab Dang ky. Extend: UC02 (tuy chon sau dat ve).</a:Comment>
</o:UseCase>
</c:UseCases>
